  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b87\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd  - \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Consular Affairs Division is fully operational on weekdays - Ministry of External Affairs",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of External Affairs has announced that the Consular Affairs Division of the Ministry of External Affairs will resume its regular services.",
        "The Ministry of External Affairs had announced on June 29 that due to the prevailing situation in the country, the Consular Affairs Division of the Ministry of External Affairs will provide services to the public only on Mondays, Wednesdays and Fridays from June 30 to July 10.",
        "However, in view of the high demand for consular services, the Consular Affairs Division will remain open to the public from Monday onwards on all weekdays to cater to general needs in this regard.",
        "The Ministry of External Affairs further informed that regional consular offices in Jaffna, Matara, Kandy, Trincomalee and Kurunegala will also follow the same working arrangements."
      ],
